service.scriptSql:
select ei.mkt_cust_inst_id, ei.task_list, ei.create_date, ei.work_type, ei.scene_type,ei.dispatch_status,ei.dispatch_group_num,
     (select staff_name from basicc_bfm_staff where state = 'A' and user_id = ei.create_staff_id) as create_staff_name,
       (select count(1) from mkt_ent_cust_inst eci where eci.mkt_cust_inst_id = ei.mkt_cust_inst_id) as cust_count,
       (select count(1) from mkt_ent_cust_locus ecl where ecl.mkt_cust_inst_id = ei.mkt_cust_inst_id and ecl.obj_type = '4') locus_count,
      concat( TRUNCATE( (select count(1) from mkt_ent_cust_locus ecl where ecl.mkt_cust_inst_id = ei.mkt_cust_inst_id and ecl.obj_type = '4')/(select count(1) from mkt_ent_cust_inst eci where eci.mkt_cust_inst_id = ei.mkt_cust_inst_id)*100,1),'%') as locus_count_rate
from mkt_ent_inst ei 
where 1=1
    <if test="createStaffId != null and createStaffId != ''">
      and ei.create_staff_id = #{createStaffId}
    </if>
    <if test="taskList != null and taskList != ''">
      and ei.task_list like  concat('%', concat(#{taskList}, '%'))
    </if>
   <if test="createdTimeStart != null and createdTimeStart != ''">
      and ei.create_date >= #{createdTimeStart}
    </if>
   <if test="createdTimeEnd != null and createdTimeEnd != ''">
      and ei.create_date <  #{createdTimeEnd}
    </if>

order by create_date desc

service.scriptSql:
SELECT DISTINCT 
  ei.mkt_cust_inst_id,
  ei.create_date,
  ei.task_list,
  ei.scene_name,
  ei.work_type,
  ei.scene_type,
  (select staff_name from basicc_bfm_staff where state = 'A' and user_id = ei.create_staff_id) as create_staff_name,
  (SELECT 
    COUNT(DISTINCT ecl.e_n_t_isnt__i_d) 
  FROM
    mkt_ent_cust_locus ecl 
  WHERE ei.mkt_cust_inst_id = ecl.mkt_cust_inst_id and  ecl.per_staff_code = 
    (select staff_code   from  basicc_bfm_staff where user_id = #{perStaffCode} )) AS pending_count,
  (SELECT 
    COUNT(DISTINCT ecl.e_n_t_isnt__i_d) 
  FROM
    mkt_ent_cust_locus ecl 
  WHERE ei.mkt_cust_inst_id = ecl.mkt_cust_inst_id 
    AND  ecl.`state_cd`='002'   and  ecl.per_staff_code = 
    (select staff_code   from  basicc_bfm_staff where user_id = #{perStaffCode} )) AS processed_count 
FROM
  mkt_ent_inst ei 
  where   EXISTS (select 1 from mkt_ent_cust_locus ecl  where ei.mkt_cust_inst_id = ecl.mkt_cust_inst_id and ecl.`state_cd`='001' and  ecl.per_staff_code = (select staff_code   from  basicc_bfm_staff where user_id = #{perStaffCode}))
        <if test="taskList != null and taskList != ''">
      and ei.task_list like  concat('%', concat(#{taskList}, '%'))
    </if>
   <if test="createdTimeStart != null and createdTimeStart != ''">
      and ei.create_date >= #{createdTimeStart}
    </if>
   <if test="createdTimeEnd != null and createdTimeEnd != ''">
      and ei.create_date <  #{createdTimeEnd}
    </if>
order by ei.create_date desc

service.scriptSql:
select distinct ei.mkt_cust_inst_id, ei.create_date, ei.task_list, ei.scene_name, ei.work_type, ei.scene_type,
    ((select count(1) from mkt_ent_cust_locus ecl where ei.mkt_cust_inst_id = ecl.mkt_cust_inst_id and ecl.state_cd = '002' and ecl.obj_type = '4')
     + (select count(1) from mkt_ent_cust_locus ecl
         left join mkt_map_rela mr on ecl.deal_type = mr.deal_type
        where ecl.state_cd = '001' and ecl.obj_type = '4' and ei.mkt_cust_inst_id = ecl.mkt_cust_inst_id and mr.per_staff_code = #{perStaffCode})
    ) as processed_count
from mkt_ent_inst ei
left join mkt_ent_cust_locus ecl on ei.mkt_cust_inst_id = ecl.mkt_cust_inst_id and ecl.state_cd = '002'
where 1=1 and (ecl.per_staff_code = #{perStaffCode} or ( #{perStaffCode} in (select mr.STAFF_ID from mkt_map_rela mr where mr.deal_type =  ecl.deal_type) and ecl.state_cd = 002))
    <if test="taskList != null and taskList != ''">
      and ei.task_list like  concat('%', concat(#{taskList}, '%'))
    </if>
   <if test="createdTimeStart != null and createdTimeStart != ''">
      and ei.create_date >= #{createdTimeStart}
    </if>
   <if test="createdTimeEnd != null and createdTimeEnd != ''">
      and ei.create_date <  #{createdTimeEnd}
    </if>
